        req:wrangle,eternal,ok
        testing
          reached:step_2
          offered:a,cards=3,crossed
          see:a magazine crossed the wire — the follower mirrors every record of the first draw with its identity intact
          see:the magazine is the catalog not the payload — each crossed card is an identity leaf while the library record it sublimed from stays streamable
          reached:revoke
          offered:b,cards=6
          refused:b
          see:the grant gates the wire — a revoked follower never received the second draw and the refusal was noted
          reached:resume
          resumed,crossed
          see:the grant is consulted live not cached — re-granting let the held-back draw cross and the follower caught up
          see:each random draw kept its own cloud across the wire — the follower holds two distinct clouds not one merged blur
